	<div class="card-body">
		<p class="lead text-center">
			<i class="fas fa-music"></i>
			<br />Sh’ma Yisrael
			<br /><span class="hebrew">יהוה</span> Elohaynu
			<br /><span class="hebrew">יהוה</span> Echad
			<br /><br />Barukh Shem k’vod
			<br />Malkhuto
			<br />L’olam Va-ed
		</p>
	</div>

	<br />

	<div class="card-header"><h5 class="text-center">Sh'ma in English</h5></div>
	<div class="card-body">
		<p class="lead text-center">
			Hear, O Israel!
			<br /><span class="hebrew">יהוה</span> is our God,
			<br /><span class="hebrew">יהוה</span> is One!

			<br /><br />Blessed is the Name
			<br />of His Glorious Kingdom
			<br />For all Eternity
		</p>
	</div>

	<br />

