			with all your heart, with all your soul, and with all your resources.
			Let these matters that I command you today be upon your heart.
			Teach them thoroughly to your children
			and speak of them while you sit in your
			home, while you walk on the way, when
			you retire, and when you arise.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="card-body">
		<p class="lead text-center">
			Bind them as a sign upon your arm and let them be tefillin between your eyes.
			And write them on the doorposts of your house and upon your gates….

			<br /><br />And you shall love your neighbor as yourself.
		</p>
	</div>

	<br />

