			<br /><sup><i class='text-muted fas fa-quote-left'></i></sup>
			<span class="text-danger">Thou shalt love YHVH Elohecha with all thy heart, and with all thy soul, and with all thy mind.</span>
			<sup><b class="text-primary">38</b></sup> <span class="text-danger">This is the first and great commandment.</span>
			<sup><b class="text-primary">39</b></sup> <span class="text-danger">And the second is like unto it, Thou shalt love thy neighbor as thyself.</span>
			<sup><b class="text-primary">40</b></sup> <span class="text-danger">On these two commandments hang all the Torah and the prophets</span> <sup><i class='text-muted fa fa-quote-right'></i></sup>.
		</p>
		<blockquote class="blockquote">
			<footer class="blockquote-footer">Messiah quoting Torah <cite title="Source Title"><b class="text-primary">Matthew 22:37-40</b></cite></footer>
		</blockquote>
	</div>

